            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Q10.  A retail manager wants answers to the following: Which category generates the highest profit? Which region performs poorly? How does sales change over time? a) Mention which charts you would use b) Identify one key insight that management could derive c) Explain how this helps in business decision-making.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' underline='true'>Answer:-</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>a) Charts to Use:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Highest profit by category:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>&#10;→ </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Bar Chart</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> (Category vs Profit) </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Poor performing region:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>&#10;→ </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Bar Chart or Map</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> (Region vs Profit) </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Sales change over time:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>&#10;→ </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Line Chart</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> (Order Date vs Sales) </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>b) One Key Insight:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Technology category</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> may generate the highest profit, while a region like </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Central or South</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> may show lower performance. Also, sales may show an increasing trend over time with some fluctuations.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>c) How this helps in business decision-making:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Helps identify </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>which products are most profitable</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Allows focus on </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>improving low-performing regions</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Supports planning using </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>sales trends over time</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Helps in better </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>resource allocation and marketing strategies</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            </formatted-text>
