    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Q.2'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='800' maxwidth='1000' minheight='800' minwidth='1000' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98000' id='3' type-v2='text' w='98400' x='800' y='1000'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Q2. After connecting to the Sample – Superstore dataset: a) List the main types of fields available (examples: time-based, geographical, numerical). b) Identify any four Dimensions and any four Measures from the dataset.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' underline='true'>Answer:-</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>a) Main types of fields available in the dataset:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>The dataset contains the following types of fields:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Time-based fields:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Order Date, Ship Date </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Geographical fields:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Country, Region, State, City </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Categorical (Text) fields:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Category, Sub-Category, Segment, Ship Mode </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Numerical fields:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Sales, Profit, Quantity, Discount </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>b) Dimensions and Measures:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>In Tableau, fields are divided into:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Dimensions (Blue fields):</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Used for categorizing data </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Measures (Green fields):</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Used for numerical calculations </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Any four Dimensions:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Category </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Sub-Category </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Region </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Ship Mode </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Any four Measures:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Sales </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Profit </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Quantity </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
